nd films, 1927-1939: a United States filmography|last=Fetrow|first=Alan G.|date=1992-08-01|publisher=McFarland|isbn=9780899505466|language=en}}</ref>\n\n== Selected filmography ==\n\n* ''[[Wild Horse Valley (film)|Wild Horse Valley]]'' (1940) \n* ''[[El Diablo Rides]]'' (1939)\n* ''[[Santa Fe Bound]]'' (1936)\n* ''[[The Speed Reporter]]'' (1936)\n* ''[[Fast Bullets]]'' (1936)\n* ''[[Texas Jack (film)|Texas Jack]]'' (1935)\n* ''[[The Judgement Book]]'' (1935)\n* ''[[The Silver Bullet (1935 film)|The Silver Bullet]]'' (1935)\n* ''[[Silent Valley (1935 film)|Silent Valley]]'' (1935)\n* ''[[Kentucky Blue Streak]]'' (1935)\n* ''[[Born to Battle (1935 film)|Born to Battle]]'' (1935)\n* ''[[Tracy Rides]]'' (1935)\n* ''[[Wolf Riders]]'' (1935)\n* ''[[Coyote Trails]]'' (1935)\n* ''[[North of Arizona]]'' (1935)\n* ''[[Loser's End]]'' (1935)\n* ''[[Unconquered Bandit]]'' (1935)\n* ''[[Terror of the Plains]]'' (1934)\n* ''[[Fighting Hero]]'' (1934)\n* ''[[Rawhide Mail]]'' (1934)\n* ''[[Mystery Ranch (1934 film)|Mystery Ranch]]'' (1934)\n* ''[[Ridin' Thru]]'' (1934)\n\n== References ==\n<references />\n\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Gordon, Rose}}\n[[Category:American women screenwriters]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing]]\n[[Category:Year of death missing]]\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rose_Gordon"}
